(3998, 'Rinvoq 30 mg 30 prolonged rel. tabs.', 'رينفوك 30مجم 30 قرص ممتد المفعول', '', '41,274', 'Upadacitinib', 'Abbvie scientific office', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', '', '30 mg', 'Upadacitinib is indicated for the treatment of moderately to severely active **rheumatoid arthritis** or active **psoriatic arthritis** in adult patients who have had an inadequate response or intolerance to one or more disease-modifying anti-rheumatic drugs (DMARDs), such as TNF blockers.[L10896, L39474] In Europe, upadacitinib may be used as monotherapy or in combination with [methotrexate] for rheumatoid or psoriatic arthritis.[L39474] 
